{"tid":901951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［係咩新玩法？］行街被人拍膊頭，唔知有冇中伏","createTime":"2018-11-14T12:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T11:55:10.000Z","uid":189277,"like":352,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"d7b3f54c9f596685a6e82ba548e3a6153d1f6b95","tid":901951,"uid":189277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:09:44.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲遇過？<br />\n頭先係葵廣毒自行行下街，行緊去地鐵站無啦啦被個男人拍膊頭問認唔認得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我呢排返工攰壓力有啲大，第一下真係以為自己認唔到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條友就話好耐冇見叫我幫下手拎埋啲嘢佢，一望係張傳單咁嘅嘢但係好奇怪係摺起咗嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我就起疑冇拎到，開始想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條友就露出馬腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續話認得我係上面棟大廈返工但問題係我冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我就雞咁腳加快速度離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再望返轉頭條友已經唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我走開咗之後就即刻check自己袋同褲袋，check哂全身，好彩又冇嘢唔見咗，又冇多咗啲可疑嘢<br />\n<br />\n有有巴絲都遇過？我都幾肯定自己冇認錯人，因為真係冇係個頭返過工，所以都幾肯定條友不懷好意，有啲不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5691192796fb85da45aee0f8c1ab49d4935e26ba","tid":901951,"uid":34256,"like":274,"dislike":16,"score":258,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"認錯人 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9430a315277c24a04136595aa9875082151b5d7e","tid":901951,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5691192796fb85da45aee0f8c1ab49d4935e26ba","tid":901951,"uid":34256,"like":274,"dislike":16,"score":258,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"認錯人 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04a61dfc7923ccf550019115c2f4493c5726e7d","tid":901951,"uid":213877,"like":141,"dislike":0,"score":141,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:17:57.000Z","msg":"迷暈煙"},{"pid":"d8092982dc4d225d316a1ac0be3b03e7525952a7","tid":901951,"uid":165012,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:19:46.000Z","msg":"叫你john jim plan"},{"pid":"e0548ea04f5c2dc52f203ce8169da00408cdab65","tid":901951,"uid":161230,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:22:03.000Z","msg":"頭先先係紅磡見到兩個女仔比個男嘅拍膊頭，唔知佢地識唔識，但係我就見到個女仔好似唔認得佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3677f45d3ec0e8f102bf5c85218261fcda3645c5","tid":901951,"uid":49918,"like":162,"dislike":4,"score":158,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:22:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e144342eb0955170187a288dfd29e2f4abf9c9c","tid":901951,"uid":189277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5691192796fb85da45aee0f8c1ab49d4935e26ba","tid":901951,"uid":34256,"like":274,"dislike":16,"score":258,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"認錯人 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:36:20.000Z","msg":"嚇死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9ad36b87cb0a996201c4202e770b8c46bcae19","tid":901951,"uid":189277,"like":63,"dislike":5,"score":58,"quote":{"pid":"3677f45d3ec0e8f102bf5c85218261fcda3645c5","tid":901951,"uid":49918,"like":162,"dislike":4,"score":158,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:22:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:37:54.000Z","msg":"但係你差我成皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbc967e5007986172ea30113a05370e0805d4c1","tid":901951,"uid":19527,"like":302,"dislike":0,"sco